<h2>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>

<p>Here's your verification code to sign in to The Art Exchange:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <div style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef7f0 0%, #ffffff 50%, #ecfdf5 100%); border: 2px solid #c10230; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 32px;">
    <div style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; color: #c10230; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
      <%= @otp_token %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p><strong>This code will expire in <%= @expires_in_minutes %> minutes.</strong></p>

<p>Enter this code on the verification page to complete your sign-in process.</p>

<p style="color: #a7a9ac; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 32px;">
  If you didn't request this verification code, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
</p>